List of features that need to be implemented (in no particular order):

* Alarm clock
* Send recommendations to many users at once
* A better UI
* History
* Support for different languages
* Add a volume bar to control the volume graphically
* Support changing the popularity of recommendations
* Configuration setting to select different decoder/sinks
* Drop down of favourite artists for similar artists radio
* Auto download of free tracks
* Add links to launch browser to go to last.fm page
* Get proxy setting from environment/maemo settings
* Notify user on successful scrobble
* Handle lastfm:// urls from non-maemo platforms
* Add option to disable confirmation dialogs
* Global hotkeys for the desktop
* Pause button
* Don't show confirmation dialogs on DBUS callbacks
* Multi-user support
